OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FStaying dry
OL,6,Fwith variable cloud and clear spells
OL,7,Finland. Becoming cloudier in the east,
OL,8,Fespecially along the coasts and on
OL,9,Fhills. Light and variable winds. A
OL,10,Fmild night.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FA cloudy start in places,
OL,13,Fespecially along the coasts, with
OL,14,Fperhaps the odd spot of light rain or
OL,15,Fdrizzle. Otherwise, dry with variable
OL,16,Fcloud and warm sunny spells. Light
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
