OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FDry
OL,6,Fwith variable cloud and bright or
OL,7,Fsunny spells Thursday. Similar
OL,8,Fconditions Friday, but breezier. A
OL,9,Fband of rain moves southeast on
OL,10,FSaturday. Temperatures will be nearer
OL,11,Fnormal.
